Package itec.minicompiler.SymbolTable

Class Summary
AddressedSymbol The AddressedSymbol implements a Symbol in the SymbolTable which has also an address in addition to the TypedSymbol-attributes.
ArrayType The ArrayType implements an ARRAY-Type in the SymbolTable.
BasicType The BasicType implements an INTEGER- or BOOLEAN-Type in the SymbolTable.
RecordType The RecordType implements a RECORD-Type in the SymbolTable.
StructuralSymbol The StructuralSymbol implements a Symbol in the SymbolTable which is used to build the structure of the SymbolTable.
Symbol The Symbol implements a Symbol in the SymbolTable.
SymbolTable The SymbolTable implements a linked list of Symbols the Parser uses to maintain the structure of the Symbols given by the source code and to do the scoping.
Type The Type implements a type a Symbol in the SymbolTable can have.
TypedSymbol The TypedSymbol implements a Symbol in the SymbolTable which has also a Type in addition to the Symbol-attributes.
ValuedSymbol The ValuedSymbol implements a Symbol in the SymbolTable which has also a value in addition to the TypedSymbol-attributes.
